flowchart TD
    A[Client Me Request] --> B[Validate JWT Token]
    B --> C{Token Valid?}
    C -->|No| D[Return 401 Unauthorized]
    C -->|Yes| E[Extract User ID from Token]
    E --> F[Check User Cache]
    F --> G{User Found in Cache?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Retrieve User Data from Cache]
    G -->|No| I[Query Database for User Info]
    I --> J[Cache User Data]
    J --> H
    H --> K[Return 200 OK with User Info]
    
    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style D fill:#ffebee
    style K fill:#e8f5e8